  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3669090/" class="title-link">伟哉！梁任公</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3669090"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2164580-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">tradition</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-11"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-11 21:34:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3669090_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最近花费４７０元搞了一套，梁任公真的是伟大，时文，杂文，论文，小说，传记无一不写。政治，思想，经济，文化，民族无一不研究。兼通中外，论及百家，中国今天这样的人物是出不了了！   晚清人物文集和全集，我已经收藏了曾文正全集，胡林翼集，左宗棠全集，李鸿章全集，彭玉...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3669090/#comments">(68回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">34有用 / 6没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3669090_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3669090_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





